<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .proposal-title {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .cta-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 8px 0 20px;
            color: #0066cc;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .signature {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 2px solid #ddd;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .lang-label {
            font-size: 0.75em;
            color: #999;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    {% set call_title = object.call.title if object.call else '' %}
    <p class="lang-label">Deutsch</p>

    <p>Hi!</p>

    <p>Wir freuen uns, dir mitzuteilen, dass deine Einreichung <span class="proposal-title">"{{ object.title }}"</span> für <span class="proposal-title">"{{ call_title }}"</span> angenommen wurde!</p>

    <p>Du wirst in Kürze weitere Mails mit Terminvorschlägen von uns erhalten.</p>

    <p>Du kannst deine Einreichung unter folgendem Link ansehen:</p>

    <a class="cta-link" href="{{ proposal_url }}">{{ proposal_url }}</a>

    <p>Bitte zögere nicht, dich bei uns zu melden, wenn du irgendwelche Fragen hast.</p>

    <p class="signature">Das {{ call_title }} Team</p>

    <hr class="divider">

    <p class="lang-label">English</p>

    <p>Hi!</p>

    <p>We are happy to let you know that your submission <span class="proposal-title">"{{ object.title }}"</span> for <span class="proposal-title">"{{ call_title }}"</span> has been accepted!</p>

    <p>You will receive further emails from us with date proposals shortly.</p>

    <p>You can view your submission at the following link:</p>

    <a class="cta-link" href="{{ proposal_url }}">{{ proposal_url }}</a>

    <p>Please don't hesitate to reach out if you have any questions.</p>

    <p class="signature">The {{ call_title }} Team</p>
</body>
</html>
